+/***************************************************************************//**
+ *   @file   imu_ros_publisher.cpp
+ *   @brief  Implementation for standard ros imu data publisher.
+ *   @author Vasile Holonec (Vasile.Holonec@analog.com)
+ *******************************************************************************
